A platform where you as a client can select from fitness coaches , dietician’s and mental health coaches, or have a combination of 2 or all. Weather it’s just fitness or holistic health, goals require skilled coaches, and at fitcru we do just that.

 Our trained and qualified coaches are ready to get you to your goals. 

As a client our world-class coaching team will be there to guide and support you every step of the way, so you can learn how to:

Yes, at fitcru, you can select a fitness coach to give you any kind of workout programs , and nutritional guidance to help you get closer to your physical fitness goals. If you’re diagnosed with any medical ailment then we recommended taking a combination of fitness coach’s and diet coaches. \nIf you’re facing any mental health isssues, then just like fitness or diet coaches , you can also select a mental health coach to help you overcome issues and reach holistic fitness.

Yes, we are a client centric company. We store your data and share it only with you and your coach. Your coaches have signed an NDA and a contact to ensure they do not share any personal information on social media or anywhere else , without your written Consent.

Yes, you can select one , two or any number of coaches as needed. A coach is a skilled professional who will help you with the right tools to make the right choices in life and get you closer to your goals.

Select the coach and duration of the plan. Fill up a health questionnaire after the purchase of the plan. Select a date and time of your first consultation with your coach.\n Once your coach consult calm is done, you coach will have all the information required about your dietary preferences and allergies , workout preferences , life commitments, work commitments etc. \nyour coaches will create a program for you which is sustainable and easily executable for you.

Based on your requirements, budget, choice of experienced coaches and location you can search any coach you want from our elite roster. \nYou can select any number of coaches from different categories to form and structure your fitness journey

Yes once you start you can change your coach within 15. Days, from any coach in the same category or you can upgrade to a higher category, more experienced coach. \nData from your consult call is recorded and shared with the new coach only once you change the coach.

Yes with our nutrition coaches / dietician’s you can get the best and the most sound diet plans for you. They will be convenient and easy to manage. Our coaches are qualified to prescribe the right supplementation if You’re willing or require to consume.

Nutrition coaching allows clients to get weekly menus, and habit coaching. \n\nIt will make deciding what’s to eat and when to eat extremely easy. Our menus have the exact portions that you need to consume.
